{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"50aef89b23","title":"对林彪在扩大的中央工作会议上的讲话稿的批语和加写的一段话","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"034ffa3453","index":0,"year":1962,"month":3,"day":20,"articleId":"50aef89b23"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"355187ef4e","type":"title","text":"对林彪在扩大的中央工作会议上的讲话稿的批语和加写的一段话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"71c2dab149","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"96af334422","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"0b5faa7342","type":"appellation","text":"田家英、罗瑞卿二同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"f163396631","type":"paragraph","text":"此件通看了一遍，是一篇很好、很有分量的文章，看了很高兴。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"8bf568eb09","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）是否应当送给林彪同志再看一遍，请瑞卿酌定。我意要送他看。如送，请瑞卿办理。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"44131ed9e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）同时送少奇、恩来、小平三同志看一遍，并征求他们的修改意见。如有修改，到北京最后酌定。如无，即交尚昆办理，不要再送我看了。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"013941e945","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）我在第一个问题部分，有一些小的修改，请你们酌定。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"502f934849","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）此件没有什么特殊秘密，可以和别的同志的讲话一同发给那些人看或者读给另一些人听。这个问题向高级中级干部保守秘密，不让他们知道、好好想一想、早作精神和物质准备，是极为有害的。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"c6395e08d3","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九六二年三月二十日上午九时","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"396ebb44a4","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"},{"id":"4b875b29e7","type":"paragraph","text":"要超过世界最强大的美国，尽多一百多年，也就可以了，因为我们的社会主义制度优胜于资本主义制度，我们的无产阶级政党——共产党的领导优胜于资产阶级政党的领导。资本主义需要三百多年才能发展到现在这样的水平，我们肯定在几十年内，至多在一百多年内，就可以赶上和超过它。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23"}],"page":{"id":"882aeb5822","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"50aef89b23","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}